{"ts":"2026-05-22T18:59:30.799Z","author":"codex-duplication-audit","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-ypqp"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"Deduplicate templates package runtime and legacy command implementation"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"Duplicate audit 2026-05-22: jscpd found src/cli/commands/templates.ts and packages/pm-templates/extensions/templates/runtime.ts carry nearly the same template normalization, option parsing, stored-template document parsing, reading, create execution, and list/apply branches. Representative clones include templates.ts:13-89 vs runtime.ts:63-138, templates.ts:89-113 vs runtime.ts:142-166, templates.ts:134-168 vs runtime.ts:180-214, and templates.ts:171-243 vs runtime.ts:211-283. Search found closed extraction item pm-2fgn and open package-first parent pm-59gj, but no active follow-up for this code drift. Fix by making the package runtime call a shared implementation or moving the legacy command to the package-backed runtime path, while preserving standalone package smoke behavior."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Chore"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":1},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["code-quality","dedup","packages","templates"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-05-22T18:59:30.799Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-05-22T18:59:30.799Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"codex-duplication-audit"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"Template name normalization, stored-template parsing, create-option mapping, and apply/list execution are single-sourced; src command and package runtime no longer diverge on template semantics; package smoke tests, templates unit tests, and pnpm build pass."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-rnpb"}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b1482